Brigadier Sabata Mokgwabone said the man was arrested after the Mahikeng Flying Squad conducted a search at his home in Golfview, Mahikeng in the early hours of Sunday morning. The search was conducted following information that was recently received about the suspect s possible involvement in illicit activities. It was during the search that 16 packets of drugs suspected to be Kat with estimated street value of R16,000 were found. The suspect was expected to appear in the Molopo Magistrate s Court in Mmabatho on Tuesday. African News Agency (ANA)